5
00:00:23.064 --> 00:00:24.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（三河）いや 確かに

6
00:00:24.399 --> 00:00:27.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
