12
00:00:42.250 --> 00:00:45.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
究極のメニュー側の承諾は
いただいております

13
00:00:46.045 --> 00:00:49.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
