21
00:01:21.289 --> 00:01:23.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
袋小路に入りやすい
日本料理に―

22
00:01:24.626 --> 00:01:29.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
野太い生命力を取り戻させる
