言葉があるけんど―

64
00:04:44.033 --> 00:04:46.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
貴いまでの艶と色やな

65
00:04:46.744 --> 00:04:49.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うーん ん？　うん

66
00:04:51.207 --> 00:04:55.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
