286
00:19:45.392 --> 00:19:46.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おいおい

287
00:19:46.518 --> 00:19:48.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
このー なに照れてんだよ

288
00:19:49.313 --> 00:19:51.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
