403
00:25:52.384 --> 00:25:53.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
カチンとくるな

404
00:25:55.011 --> 00:25:57.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
