414
00:26:26.876 --> 00:26:28.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
できるもんか

415
00:26:28.295 --> 00:26:32.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
世界中の国が 日本の科学技術と
