431
00:27:37.822 --> 00:27:38.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
なんですって？

432
00:27:39.991 --> 00:27:42.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
