434
00:27:44.954 --> 00:27:48.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
今 何時だと思ってんだ！
昼だそ昼！

435
00:27:48.458 --> 00:27:50.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
昨日 ちょっと
飲みすぎちゃいまして

436
00:27:51.503 --> 00:27:52.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
山岡！

437
00:27:52.879 --> 00:27:53.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
