447
00:28:26.496 --> 00:28:28.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そりゃあ大変だ

448
00:28:28.248 --> 00:28:32.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
