459
00:29:07.454 --> 00:29:08.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
山岡！

460
00:29:09.038 --> 00:29:12.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
その場にいながら 何も
