482
00:30:13.978 --> 00:30:14.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（山岡）ついてくりゃ 分かる

483
00:30:19.234 --> 00:30:20.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（角丸）むう…

484
00:30:20.568 --> 00:30:24.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
今度ばかりは アメリカ側の
