私もそのように申したのですが

502
00:31:17.584 --> 00:31:20.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ぜひともこれを
副総理に届けるようにと…

503
00:31:21.045 --> 00:31:21.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何？

504
00:31:25.675 --> 00:31:26.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
これは！

505
00:31:29.637 --> 00:31:30.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（角丸）おお

