1167
01:13:17.184 --> 01:13:19.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そろそろ訳を説明してくれ

1168
01:13:19.520 --> 01:13:25.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
その前に この猿の楽園の飼育係の
